strings.Value: "I'm perfectly fine, just a bit tired. A little sleep and I'll be back on my feet again."
"Don't look at me like that. I'm just a little out of sorts."
"You need help, Valerie. Stop being so proud â€” we can all see you're suffering!"
"That's the spirit! Not like those southern wussies who run to the healer after every sneeze!"
"Show yourself some mercy, Valerie. Sometimes it's more important to be honest about your weaknesses than it is to be brave."
"Well, you have a strong character, that's for sure."
